---
const WA_HREF = "https://wa.me/5527997402481?text=Hi%21%20I%27d%20like%20to%20book%20a%20free%20automation%20audit.";
---

<section class="section-blue">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-block">
      <span class="kicker">Ready to get your time back?</span>
      <h2 style={{color:'#fff'}}>Book your free automation audit call</h2>
      <p class="subhead" style={{color:'rgba(255,255,255,0.85)', maxWidth:560}}>
        In 45 minutes, we'll map your biggest bottlenecks and hand you a custom roadmap — whether you hire us or not.
      </p>
      <div style={{display:'flex', gap:12, flexWrap:'wrap', justifyContent:'center'}}>
        <a class="btn btn-dark btn-lg" href={WA_HREF} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a call →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="#systems">See what we build</a>
      </div>
      <p style={{color:'rgba(255,255,255,0.65)', fontSize:14, margin:0}}>No commitment. No sales pressure. Just a clear roadmap for your business.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
